经济学奖得主在内的众多经济学家就曾联名写信，呼吁选民不要投票给特朗普，原因之一就是他的经济计划。 这一次，这些知名专家承认哈里斯和特朗普的经济计划尚不「完全」为人所知，但他们表示，两人的言论和「过去的所作所为」足以说明问题。 （参考消息） 内容来源 23 名诺贝尔经济学奖得主公开支持哈里斯 _ 特朗普 _ 西蒙·约翰逊 _ 计划"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-e6c656da34e6b3250eddea9a5067163a_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "3.1 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1925713761"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIxKfVxqLTovRUEAMaCTExMTM2MTc3MSDLoei4BjAAOLAEQAtyCjE5MjU3MTM3NjF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1729898542.410717", "card_id": "Q_1890421174", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 59}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待《鸣潮》因产能不足，致使接下来几个版本只能出单个新五星角色的问题，这会为游戏带来哪些影响？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-c7c16355707ee6007b694af461b458a2_l.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "3.1 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1890421174"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIxKfVxqLTovRUEAMaCTExMTM1NDgwOSDI0+a4BjAAOElADHIKMTg5MDQyMTE3NHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "13_1729898542.410914", "card_id": "Q_1949241055", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 62}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待天猫双 11 数码家电商品持续享受国补优惠活动？消费者都能获得哪些真实惠？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "天猫双 11 数码家电超优惠，给你的购物车亿点震撼！政府补贴碰撞天猫双 11，最高叠加 5 重优惠，低至 6 折。快来查收超全攻略~"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-555b7e28eb3888bbfca7e6749eab30f3_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "3.1 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1949241055